title: Stop In The Name Of Trends 1/12: Mike Pompeo, Sheldon Adelson, Chuck Norris, Trinity Rodman
itunes:title: Stop In The Name Of Trends 1/12: Mike Pompeo, Sheldon Adelson, Chuck Norris, Trinity Rodman
description:
On this edition of Stop In The Name Of Trends Jack and Miles discuss Mike Pompeo cancelling his Euro trip because foreign leaders refused to meet with him, Sheldon Adelson has passed, a Chuck Norris look-a-like at the Capitol storming, and Trinity Rodman has declared for the NWSL draft!
